item.title: about me
item.description: A bigger pleasure than reading a book is re-reading it. Hey there! I hope you’re having a good day. My name is Zakatell and thank you for visiting my site. If you stumbled here then you probably found my post intriguing or wanna know me a little. Here’s some small details: A software developer currently working for engageSPARK. It’s an amazing company with awesome people, come join us.
